comments: Harris (BKN) legally contests Crowder's (PHX) jump shot attempt.

Johnson (BKN) makes inadvertent contact with Bridges' (PHX) face during the rebound.  Contact to an opponent?s head/face can be deemed marginal when the result of a natural basketball move, provided the contact is not disproportionate or uncontrolled.
Green (BKN) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Booker's (PHX) path and does not deliver any contact.
Ayton (PHX) makes hand on ball contact with Harden (BKN) during Harden's driving shot attept.
Bridges (PHX) makes marginal contact with Shamet (BKN) as the pick concludes and Bridges begins to roll.
Replay review of the foul called on Harden (BKN) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful.  Harden reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball while defending Booker (PHX).
Harden (BKN) makes marginal contact with Bridges (PHX) as the engage and disengage prior to the pick.
Harden (BKN) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Ayton's (PHX) path.
Ayton (PHX) slides a hand across Green's (BKN) front at the end of the drive and does not affect his SQBR.
Crowder (PHX) swipes and misses during Green's (BKN) driving shot attempt.
Shamet (BKN) makes brush contact with Paul's (PHX) arm at the start of his rip-through.
Paul (PHX) slightly extends his off-arm as he stops and spins away from Harden (BKN) during the drive.
Harris (BKN) legally contests Bridges' (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Bridges (PHX) legally contests Harden's (BKN) jump shot attempt.
Paul (PHX) firms up in Green's (BKN) path and makes marginal contact with Green during the pick.
Shamet (BKN) maintains a legal guarding position and absorbs the marginal contact initiated by Booker (PHX) during the drive.
Shamet (BKN) maintains a legal vertical defensive position during Booker's (PHX) shot attempt.
Harden (BKN) and Ayton (PHX) engage and disengage with each prior to Ayton tipping the rebound away from Harden.
Harden (BKN) makes marginal contact with Bridges (PHX) as they move during the inbound play.
Booker (PHX) makes contact to Harden's (BKN) face when he reaches in.  There is no clear and conclusive video evidence to confirm that Booker avoids making contact.
Shamet (BKN) legally contests Paul's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
